title: Rain is important for how carbon dioxide affects grasslands

title_detail.value: Rain is important for how carbon dioxide affects grasslands

summary: Vegetation biomass on grasslands increases in response to elevated carbon dioxide levels, but less than expected. Vegetation on grasslands with a wet spring season has the greatest increase.
